languages.text: "Вот и хорошо, вот и славно. Ребята вас проводят. И не волнуйтесь — вам ничего, совсем ничего не угрожает!"
"Ah, that's good, very good. The lads will escort you. And don't worry — no harm will come to you, none at all!"

languages.text: “啊，很好，非常好。这些小伙子们会带你离开。别担心，你不会受到伤害，一点都不会！”
languages.original_text: "Ah, that's good, very good. The lads will escort you. And don't worry — no harm will come to you, none at all!"

languages.text: «Ah, bien, bien. Los muchachos te escoltarán. Y no te preocupes, ¡no te pasará nada en absoluto!».
languages.original_text: "Ah, that's good, very good. The lads will escort you. And don't worry — no harm will come to you, none at all!"

languages.text: 「よーしよし。野郎どもがあんたを案内するよ。あんたには指一本触れさせないから安心しろ！」
languages.original_text: "Ah, that's good, very good. The lads will escort you. And don't worry — no harm will come to you, none at all!"

traits.locale_text: 「よーしよし。野郎どもがあんたを案内するよ。あんたには指一本触れさせないから安心しろ！」

languages.text: "Ah, das ist gut, sehr gut. Die Jungs begleiten Euch. Und keine Sorge – Euch wird nichts zustoßen, nicht das Geringste!"
languages.original_text: "Ah, that's good, very good. The lads will escort you. And don't worry — no harm will come to you, none at all!"

languages.text: « Excellent. Mes hommes vont vous escorter. Et ne vous inquiétez pas, il ne vous sera fait aucun mal ! »
